<section class="sec"><div class="wrap"><div class="steps"><div class="srow rv"><span class="sn">01</span><h3>Web &amp; SaaS Platforms</h3><span class="sd">Custom platforms, dashboards, CRM/ERP and internal tools — engineered to scale.</span><span class="ar"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"/></svg></span></div><div class="srow rv"><span class="sn">02</span><h3>Mobile Applications</h3><span class="sd">iOS and Android — native and cross-platform, finished to flagship quality.</span><span class="ar"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"/></svg></span></div><div class="srow rv"><span class="sn">03</span><h3>AI Solutions</h3><span class="sd">Agents, copilots and AI-native features that ship to production.</span><span class="ar"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"/></svg></span></div><div class="srow rv"><span class="sn">04</span><h3>E-Commerce</h3><span class="sd">Shopify and custom commerce — storefronts, integrations and automation.</span><span class="ar"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"/></svg></span></div><div class="srow rv"><span class="sn">05</span><h3>Automation</h3><span class="sd">Workflows that remove the manual work across your business.</span><span class="ar"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"/></svg></span></div><div class="srow rv"><span class="sn">06</span><h3>Product Strategy</h3><span class="sd">Discovery, UX, architecture and roadmapping for the AI era.</span><span class="ar"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"/></svg></span></div></div></div></section>
